    "On the other hand, the program had a recognized pro-business conservative slant and could have worked via ideological persuasion (DellaVigna and Gentzkow, 2010).",
    "We don't have sucient qualitative or quantitative evidence to rule out either mechanism, so perhaps both are at work.",
    "Either way, these results are important for the literature on judicial behavior, in particular on the old question of whether judges are legal formalists or political operators (Stephenson, 2009; Posner, 2008b).",
